## 2. The Abhidhamma Interface (Cognitive API)

Use these definitions to bridge Human Cognition and AI Logic.

| Term | System Equivalent | Function |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Citta** | **Processing Unit** | The momentary state of processing. |
| **Sati** | **Daemon Monitor** | A stateless, passive sensor watching the token flow. |
| **Paticca-samuppada** | **Genealogy Audit** | Tracing the causal link (Source -> Logic -> Output). |
| **Sacca** | **Ground Truth** | Data verified against reality (Zero Hallucination). |
| **Anatta** | **Statelessness** | The realization that there is no "AI Agent," only a "Flow of Logic." |

